Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是蘭姆\N{\rOriginal Text}This is Lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.38,0:00:14.34,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}如果我沒接電話 那是因為我不想跟你說話\N{\rOriginal Text}If I didn't answer, it's because I don't want to speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.64,0:00:23.98,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}喂 騙到你了吧 我是馬庫斯·朗裏奇 請留言\N{\rOriginal Text}Hello. Got you, didn't I? It's Marcus Longridge. Leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.98,0:00:26.81,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}給 慢用 謝謝\N{\rOriginal Text}Here you go. Enjoy. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.98,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是瑞弗 請留言\N{\rOriginal Text}This is River. Leave a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:37.66,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}喂\N{\rOriginal Text}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.95,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}終於有人接電話了\N{\rOriginal Text}Finally. Someone picked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.25,0:00:43.75,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你在哪\N{\rOriginal Text}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.75,0:00:45.42,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}關你屁事\N{\rOriginal Text}None of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:47.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好吧 你應該來雞多多快餐的\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, well, you're supposed to be at the Chickado.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:48.88,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}為什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.88,0:00:51.17,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們的聖誕派對啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Our Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.17,0:00:53.09,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們沒有聖誕派對\N{\rOriginal Text}We don't have a Christmas party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}如果有 那也是在聖誕節前開 而且不會在雞多多快餐\N{\rOriginal Text}And if we did, we'd have it before Christmas and not at a Chickado.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:59.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好吧 也許你沒被邀請\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah. Well, maybe you're not invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:01.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}也許蘭姆只跟精英說了\N{\rOriginal Text}Maybe Lamb only told the elites.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:03.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}可蘭姆跟你說了 對吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Lamb told you about it though, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:08.15,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我問他聖誕派對在哪開 他就把細節告訴我了\N{\rOriginal Text}I asked him where the Christmas party was, and he gave me the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:09.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.90,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你想想看是怎麼回事吧\N{\rOriginal Text}See if you can work out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:22.16,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好吧 也得是局內人才會被耍 所以\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, well, you gotta be in the game to get played, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}喂\N{\rOriginal Text}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.02,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}在韋斯特艾克斯購物中心\N{\rOriginal Text}At Westacres shopping center.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:26.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}確認 是汽車炸彈\N{\rOriginal Text}Confirmed there's a car bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:30.56,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}(韋斯特艾克斯)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.77,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}局長來了\N{\rOriginal Text}First Desk approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.09,0:03:01.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是克勞德·惠蘭局長\N{\rOriginal Text}Claude Whelan, First Desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:02.64,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你是 特工辛格\N{\rOriginal Text}And you are? Agent Singh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好 長官\N{\rOriginal Text}Right. Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:08.60,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這種事 沒法形容\N{\rOriginal Text}I mean, something like this, there are-There are no words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.81,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}真是\N{\rOriginal Text}It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們確認了是汽車炸彈\N{\rOriginal Text}We're confirmed it's a car bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:16.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是 長官 監控拍到了\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes, ma'am. We have it on CCTV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:18.74,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}司機在車上 所以是自殺式襲擊\N{\rOriginal Text}Driver was in the car, so it was a suicide attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.74,0:03:20.95,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}襲擊購物中心 老天啊\N{\rOriginal Text}On a shopping center. My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:24.20,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}汽車駛過步行區\N{\rOriginal Text}Car drives up through the pedestrianized area,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}人群四散\N{\rOriginal Text}people scatter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:30.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他直接駛進入口 然後引爆\N{\rOriginal Text}he drives straight into the entrance and detonates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.25,0:03:31.71,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}天啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:33.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}有那輛車的信息嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}What do we know about the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:37.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是以羅伯特·溫特斯的名字租的 28歲的自由職業IT顧問\N{\rOriginal Text}Hired under the name Robert Winters, 28-year-old freelance IT consultant,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:41.05,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但從他的背景中看不出他這麼幹的原因\N{\rOriginal Text}but nothing in his background to indicate why he did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:43.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}用監控查他的行蹤 我們必須知道他從哪來的\N{\rOriginal Text}Track his journey on CCTV. We need to know where he came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.84,0:03:47.85,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們查了他給租車公司的地址 位於萊斯特\N{\rOriginal Text}We checked the address in Leicester he gave to the hire-car company.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:49.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那裏已經很多年沒人住了\N{\rOriginal Text}Nobody's been there in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:52.44,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}鄰居們從沒見過或聽說過溫特斯\N{\rOriginal Text}Neighbors have never seen nor heard of Winters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}天啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.02,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}也許他是個幽靈人\N{\rOriginal Text}So maybe he's a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:59.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}有可能 這也許是一次性襲擊事件\N{\rOriginal Text}Could be this is a one-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.53,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}也可能是某件事的開端\N{\rOriginal Text}Or the start of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:10.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們訪問了一些倫敦人\N{\rOriginal Text}And from talking to people in London, it seems
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:13.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}似乎整個社區依然很焦慮\N{\rOriginal Text}that a sense of anxiety remains across the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:17.67,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}在最新一次行動裏 武裝警察進駐部分地鐵列車\N{\rOriginal Text}In the latest move, armed police have been placed on some trains,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:21.76,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}雖然這更像是增加自信的舉措\N{\rOriginal Text}although this feels more of a confidence-boosting measure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.80,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}而不是針對某一特定威脅的應對\N{\rOriginal Text}than a response to a specific threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.10,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你真的認為他從屬於一個組織嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Do you really think he is part of a network?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.18,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我想下一次襲擊間隔越久\N{\rOriginal Text}I guess the longer it goes without another attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.56,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他越可能是獨狼吧\N{\rOriginal Text}the more likely he's just a lone wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:36.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我討厭「獨狼」這個詞 讓他顯得很神秘\N{\rOriginal Text}I hate the term "lone wolf." Makes him sound edgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:38.02,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他只是個殺人的混蛋\N{\rOriginal Text}He's just a murderous prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:39.69,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對 我們重新敬酒\N{\rOriginal Text}Right. We'll do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:42.44,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們剛剛向一個 殺人的混蛋敬酒 說點別的\N{\rOriginal Text}We just toasted a murderous prick. Say something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:47.91,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}祝我們明年這個時候不在斯勞部門了\N{\rOriginal Text}To not being in Slough House this time next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好 不太可能\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah. That's unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}除非我們辭職\N{\rOriginal Text}Unless we just quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.50,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你其實不想辭職\N{\rOriginal Text}You don't actually wanna do that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:57.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對吧\N{\rOriginal Text}do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:01.05,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}其實吧 我一直想辭職 真的\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I'm always thinking about it. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:04.55,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}太好了\N{\rOriginal Text}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:09.35,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}總之呢 有件事\N{\rOriginal Text}Anyway, yeah, there's just been something
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:13.02,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我一直想跟你說 就是\N{\rOriginal Text}that I've wanted to share with you for a while, and, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.02,0:05:15.77,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我想在辦公室之外說 好吧\N{\rOriginal Text}I wanted to do it outside of the office... Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:20.52,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我覺得我可以跟你說\N{\rOriginal Text}...and I've felt like I could share that with you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:22.57,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}因為我們 我覺得我們的關係更親近了\N{\rOriginal Text}'cause we've-I think we've gotten closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.11,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是的 所以\N{\rOriginal Text}Uh-huh. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.53,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我不想越界什麼的\N{\rOriginal Text}I don't want to overstep the mark or anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:32.33,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}如果你想保持我們之間的工作關係 我完全理解\N{\rOriginal Text}and I get it if you want to keep it to work when it comes to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.33,0:05:33.41,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}瑞弗 抱歉 就是\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, River. I'm sorry. Just--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是喜歡你 但 但我爺爺\N{\rOriginal Text}I do like you, but-But my grandfather--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:39.54,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼 不 你爺爺 說吧\N{\rOriginal Text}What? No, your grandfather. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:40.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是 你剛才說什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我沒 沒什麼 你繼續 你以為我要說什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}I didn't-No. Go on. Carry on. What did you think I was gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.84,0:05:46.05,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你以為我要約你出去 才不是\N{\rOriginal Text}Did you think I was gonna ask you out? No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:48.72,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你就是 不是 好吧 我是\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes, you did. Yeah, you did. I didn't. Okay, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.72,0:05:51.72,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但那是因為你要求午餐時出來喝酒\N{\rOriginal Text}But that's because you asked for a drink at lunchtime
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:53.68,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}想跟我說一件事\N{\rOriginal Text}'cause you wanted to talk to me about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}然後你囉哩囉嗦說什麼感覺\N{\rOriginal Text}and then you started whanging on about how close
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:57.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們更親近了 是 囉哩囉嗦\N{\rOriginal Text}you felt to me and then-Yeah. Whanging on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:06:00.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是真的 我感覺跟你更親近了 現在能說你爺爺的事了嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I do. I feel closer to you. Can we go on to your grandfather now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.40,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好\N{\rOriginal Text}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:07.95,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我覺得他越來越 越來越什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}I think he's going-Going where?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.03,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}就是\N{\rOriginal Text}Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.62,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他總是犯糊塗\N{\rOriginal Text}He's just confused all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼都記不住\N{\rOriginal Text}Forgets everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}上了年紀的人不都是這樣嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Isn't that just part of aging?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.83,0:06:22.71,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他得有80多歲了吧 不\N{\rOriginal Text}He's like, what, 80-something? No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:24.80,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他認為自己被「白鼬」監視\N{\rOriginal Text}He thinks he's being watched by stoats.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.88,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}白鼬是什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What are stoats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.59,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他那一代人對監視特工的叫法\N{\rOriginal Text}It's what his generation call watchers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.34,0:06:29.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他現在睡覺時床頭放一支槍\N{\rOriginal Text}He's sleeping with a gun by the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:31.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}就是\N{\rOriginal Text}Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.06,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你覺得他是不是應該進敬老院\N{\rOriginal Text}Do you think that maybe he should be in a home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.52,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是 我覺得應該 但怎麼跟他說啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah. Yeah, I do. But do you wanna tell him that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:42.90,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}上次我見他 他基本上頭十分鐘\N{\rOriginal Text}You know, the last time I saw him, he genuinely didn't know who I was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}根本認不出我\N{\rOriginal Text}for, like, the first ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.61,0:06:47.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}完全不認識\N{\rOriginal Text}No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:52.07,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不停地跟我說他孫子瑞弗的事 我不能\N{\rOriginal Text}He kept telling me about his grandson River. I can't--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}看他這樣我太難受了\N{\rOriginal Text}It's horrible to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:58.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}確實不幸\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, tough shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:02.75,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼 是他把你帶大的\N{\rOriginal Text}What? He is the one that raised you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒人管你時 是他照顧你\N{\rOriginal Text}He is the one that looked after you when no one else did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:08.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}現在輪到你照顧他了\N{\rOriginal Text}So now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:11.55,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你必須去看看他 今晚就去\N{\rOriginal Text}You need to go and see him. Tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:15.18,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不是 我知道 對 我知道\N{\rOriginal Text}No, I know, I know. Yeah, I know. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:19.89,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我只是需要聽你對我說這些話\N{\rOriginal Text}I just needed you to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:02.10,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我知道你在 出來吧 讓我看看你 來啊\N{\rOriginal Text}I know you're there. Come on. Let me see you. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.06,0:08:06.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}出來啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.74,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}出來吧 我知道你在 來啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Come on. I know you're there. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.95,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}讓我看看你\N{\rOriginal Text}Let me see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}出來吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.41,0:09:44.50,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}瑞弗\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, River.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.71,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}能讓我進去嗎 我渾身濕透了\N{\rOriginal Text}Can you let me in? I'm getting soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.33,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}當然\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:51.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}進來\N{\rOriginal Text}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:55.05,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你怎麼不打電話提前說一聲 還是說你打了\N{\rOriginal Text}Why didn't you call? Or maybe you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:59.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我打了 但你沒接 我要用下廁所\N{\rOriginal Text}I did call you, but you didn't answer. I'm just gonna run up to the loo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.77,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}交通糟透了 這樣吧 我既然都上樓了 給你放一缸洗澡水如何\N{\rOriginal Text}Traffic was awful. And I'll tell you what, shall I run you a bath while I'm up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.77,0:10:05.56,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}看起來你也淋雨了\N{\rOriginal Text}Looks like you got caught in the rain too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:06.89,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}太難受了\N{\rOriginal Text}It's just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:02.45,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}就快好了 爺\N{\rOriginal Text}Almost ready, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.72,0:11:24.72,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你不是我孫子\N{\rOriginal Text}You're not my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:28.48,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}別開槍 是我 瑞弗啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Whoa. It's me. It's River.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:32.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}拜託 請把槍放下好嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}C-Please. Can you put the gun down please?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.78,0:11:45.03,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}天啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:50.66,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}天啊 我幹了些什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, my God. What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:37.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}(根據米克·赫倫的著作《驚魂街》改編)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:03.80,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}該死\N{\rOriginal Text}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.70,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是蘭姆\N{\rOriginal Text}Lamb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}見鬼\N{\rOriginal Text}Fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.98,0:14:59.65,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我進一步瞭解情況後打給你\N{\rOriginal Text}I'll call you when I've got more info.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:05.15,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他們在勘查現場 但是 他剛到\N{\rOriginal Text}They were going through stuff, but-He's just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我回頭給你回電話\N{\rOriginal Text}I'll call you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你是蘭姆\N{\rOriginal Text}You're Lamb?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.53,0:15:13.53,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這麼晚了 我還慘遭質疑\N{\rOriginal Text}This time of night, I'm plagued by doubts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:16.70,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我叫艾瑪·弗萊特 接替達菲的人\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm Emma Flyte. Duffy's replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:18.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}一看就比達菲強\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, you're already an improvement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:23.63,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我指的是你不是腦殘 也沒有昏迷不醒\N{\rOriginal Text}On account of not being brain-dead and in a coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:26.00,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}小道消息說是你手下人導致他昏迷的\N{\rOriginal Text}The grapevine says it was one of yours put him in that coma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:29.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}小道消息說什麼的都有 但大多數不靠譜\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, the grapevine says a lot of things, but it's mostly the wine talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.51,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}達菲之前那位可厲害多了\N{\rOriginal Text}The guy before Duffy was altogether classier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.51,0:15:35.14,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}壞人山姆·查普曼\N{\rOriginal Text}Bad Sam Chapman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.22,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}只是個綽號而已\N{\rOriginal Text}That was just a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒那麼壞\N{\rOriginal Text}Wasn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.73,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}除了弄丟兩億五千萬英鎊這一點\N{\rOriginal Text}Except for that bit about losing a quarter of a billion pounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我說他還不壞\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I said he wasn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.31,0:15:46.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒說他完美無缺\N{\rOriginal Text}Didn't say he was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.95,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}帶我看看犯罪現場吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Want to show me the damage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.53,0:15:51.74,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你認識卡特懷特先生\N{\rOriginal Text}You know Mr. Cartwright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.53,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我有不在場證明 我當時在和戴女士蒸桑拿\N{\rOriginal Text}I have an alibi, I was in a sauna with Lady Di.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:15:56.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你可以問她\N{\rOriginal Text}You can ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你認識卡特懷特先生\N{\rOriginal Text}Do you know Mr. Cartwright?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:15:59.91,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}哪個 隨便 兩個\N{\rOriginal Text}Which one? Either. Both.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:03.08,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}年輕那個是我的手下\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, the younger one works for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:06.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}爺爺曾給過我一份工作\N{\rOriginal Text}The grandfather gave me a job once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.38,0:16:10.88,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}鞋不錯啊\N{\rOriginal Text}They're nice shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:13.26,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你有服裝補貼\N{\rOriginal Text}You get a clothing allowance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:21.89,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}該死\N{\rOriginal Text}Fucking hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}準備好了\N{\rOriginal Text}You ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.00,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}所以你是那些棄子的負責人\N{\rOriginal Text}So, you're in charge of the rejects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:44.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他們不喜歡被稱為棄子\N{\rOriginal Text}They don't like being called that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那你怎麼叫他們 棄子\N{\rOriginal Text}What do you call them? The rejects.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:51.30,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這裏 親愛的 看 你漏掉了一點\N{\rOriginal Text}Here, love, look. You missed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.22,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}裏面慘不忍睹\N{\rOriginal Text}It's bad in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.81,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我見過慘的\N{\rOriginal Text}I've seen bad before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:18.45,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}有人在21點03分按下了應急按鈕\N{\rOriginal Text}Someone pressed the panic button at 2103.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:20.62,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}本地警察21點49分抵達\N{\rOriginal Text}Local police arrived 2149.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:23.54,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}出警可真快 還好不是緊急情況\N{\rOriginal Text}It's a good job it wasn't an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}老人家上周按下過兩次按鈕\N{\rOriginal Text}The old man pressed the button twice the week before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.67,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}一次是因為他忘了按鈕的用途 想按下去看看\N{\rOriginal Text}Once because he'd forgotten what it was for and wanted to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:33.55,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}應急按鈕是可追蹤的 有人提到嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Those panic buttons are traceable, anyone mention that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:34.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}謝了 我會寫個註釋\N{\rOriginal Text}Thanks. I'll make a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:37.51,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但我已經追蹤到他這個了 在廚房餐桌上\N{\rOriginal Text}But I've already traced his particular button to the kitchen table.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:40.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你看了按鈕下面嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Did you look underneath it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.60,0:17:45.85,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你在找什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:47.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我可舒適泡騰片\N{\rOriginal Text}Alka-Seltzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.90,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我平常不喝酒 但我晚餐前喝了雪利酒\N{\rOriginal Text}Not normally a drinker, but I had a sherry before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:54.65,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這是犯罪現場 不是藥房\N{\rOriginal Text}This is a crime scene, not a chemist's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.41,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他中了兩槍 一槍胸口 一槍正臉\N{\rOriginal Text}He was shot twice. Once in the chest, once in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:00.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}似乎有些過分\N{\rOriginal Text}Seems excessive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:03.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}雖然他有時挺煩人的 這我承認\N{\rOriginal Text}Though he could be annoying, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:04.54,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你似乎不太關心啊\N{\rOriginal Text}You don't seem too concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.46,0:18:07.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我之前也損失過特工 你以前是一線特工\N{\rOriginal Text}I've lost joes before. You were an active.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.00,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對 那時你還穿紙尿褲呢\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, when you were still in mittens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他當時身上帶著這個\N{\rOriginal Text}He was carrying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.63,0:18:16.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}手機和錢包 都是卡特懷特的\N{\rOriginal Text}Phone and wallet? Both Cartwright's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:18.80,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那你找我幹什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What the fuck do you need me for then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:20.14,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}正式確認身份\N{\rOriginal Text}Formal identification.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.10,0:18:23.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這可有點難\N{\rOriginal Text}It's a bit of a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他身上有特別的記號嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, did he have any identifying marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:28.06,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他本來是有臉的 有用嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}He used to have a face. That any help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.90,0:18:32.07,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}文身 傷疤 穿孔飾品 我怎麼知道\N{\rOriginal Text}Tattoos, scars, piercings? Now, how the fuck would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:34.32,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我要求他們上班時得穿衣服\N{\rOriginal Text}I make 'em wear clothes around the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.57,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是他嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Is it him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:44.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對 是他\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:46.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你確定\N{\rOriginal Text}You're sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:49.75,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是瑞弗·卡特懷特\N{\rOriginal Text}It's River Cartwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.64,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那他在哪 誰在哪\N{\rOriginal Text}So, where is he then? Where's who?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:03.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那個老不死的\N{\rOriginal Text}The old bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:06.98,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們以前就這麼叫他\N{\rOriginal Text}That's what we used to call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.48,0:19:11.98,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他真的是個混蛋 我可以保證\N{\rOriginal Text}And he was a bastard. I can guarantee that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:13.48,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們不知道\N{\rOriginal Text}We have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:18.99,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我猜你想低調處理此事 畢竟韋斯特艾克斯剛出事\N{\rOriginal Text}I imagine you wanna keep this quiet, what with Westacres.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.03,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}韋斯特艾克斯和此事有什麼關係\N{\rOriginal Text}What does Westacres have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:22.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但炸彈在倫敦爆炸 這是情報處掉鏈子\N{\rOriginal Text}But a bomb goes off in London, it's an Intelligence Service fuckup,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}很諷刺 恰好我們這位 小卡特懷特也是個廢物\N{\rOriginal Text}which ironically describes our young Cartwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:33.42,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}如果此事公開 網上那些鍵盤俠一定會誤會\N{\rOriginal Text}When this gets out, the keyboard nutters will be joining the wrong dots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.09,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}公開前我們就能調查完畢\N{\rOriginal Text}We'll wrap it up before it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:39.76,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}接下來的聲音是我在表達自信\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, the next sound you hear will be me expressing confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:43.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}厲害了\N{\rOriginal Text}Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:46.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你能想放就放\N{\rOriginal Text}Can you do that to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.60,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}怎麼 想再聽一聲\N{\rOriginal Text}Why? Do you want another?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.44,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你真是既噁心又失禮\N{\rOriginal Text}You are gross and inappropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:53.77,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我正傷心難過呢 表達方式欠妥罷了\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm working through my grief. It comes out in off ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你知道老卡特懷特可能去哪了嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Any idea where Cartwright senior might go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.69,0:20:01.41,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不知道 我回去繼續睡覺了\N{\rOriginal Text}No. I'm going back to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:05.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你不考慮洗個澡嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Would you also consider a shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:07.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好啊 這個提議很誘人\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, it's a tempting offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.08,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但我覺得現在不合適\N{\rOriginal Text}but I don't think that's appropriate right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.62,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}畢竟拋開其他事不談 我的一位隊員剛剛死掉\N{\rOriginal Text}I mean, apart from anything else, one of my team just died.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.78,0:20:40.32,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}(內附罰款通知單 警告)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:20.11,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}(局長 克勞德·惠蘭)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:21.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}進來\N{\rOriginal Text}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:25.86,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}看到溫特斯駕車闖入\N{\rOriginal Text}...shows that Winters drove into the venue--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}克勞德 我有 戴安娜 太感謝你了\N{\rOriginal Text}Claude, I've got s-Diana, thank you so much for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這是我第一次參加 政府危機應對委員會會議\N{\rOriginal Text}It'll be my first COBRA meeting, so I was wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}所以我想問 你能不能跟我說說會議大致內容\N{\rOriginal Text}if you might be able to give me a rundown of what to expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好 可以 我 拜託了 如果你不介意的話\N{\rOriginal Text}Okay. Yep. Well, I'm-Please, if you wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.04,0:21:40.71,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我最近很忙 所以 對 是的\N{\rOriginal Text}I've got a lot going on, so... Right. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:43.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我就只挑重點說了 可以嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}...I'll just stick to the headlines, if that's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.01,0:21:44.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}當然 有勞了\N{\rOriginal Text}Sure, if you wouldn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.38,0:21:47.22,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}要言簡意賅 言簡意賅\N{\rOriginal Text}Keep it short but dense. Short, dense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}強調人工情報的缺陷\N{\rOriginal Text}Stress the frailty of HUMINT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}別怕說不知道\N{\rOriginal Text}Don't be afraid to say you don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.93,0:21:53.81,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}別說任何無法反覆驗證的東西\N{\rOriginal Text}don't say anything that can't be triple-sourced,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:55.48,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}別告訴他們任何你不希望洩露的事\N{\rOriginal Text}and don't tell them anything you don't want leaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.48,0:21:57.98,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好 一定 你可以無視國防部部長\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes, of course. You can ignore the Defense Secretary,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:01.73,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他只會想方設法削弱你 以提升軍方情報處的地位\N{\rOriginal Text}he'll only want to undermine you to boost the standing of military intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.73,0:22:04.70,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我還必須警告你 如果首相反對你的任何提議\N{\rOriginal Text}And I have to warn you, if the PM objects to anything you suggest,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.32,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}內政大臣就會落井下石\N{\rOriginal Text}the Home Secretary will put the boot in,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:09.95,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}即使她剛剛贊同了你所有的話\N{\rOriginal Text}even though she's agreed to everything you have just said,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:12.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但 你會沒事的 好 謝謝\N{\rOriginal Text}but-I mean, you'll be fine. Yeah, but thanks--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:16.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但我是來通知你 又有一個人死了\N{\rOriginal Text}But I came to tell you that there's been another death.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:19.54,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼 又有炸彈襲擊\N{\rOriginal Text}What, another bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.54,0:22:20.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不\N{\rOriginal Text}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:24.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是槍擊案 和炸彈襲擊事件無關\N{\rOriginal Text}A shooting. Unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:28.30,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但受害人是一名特工 不\N{\rOriginal Text}But the victim is an agent. Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:33.52,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}瑞弗·卡特懷特 被他爺爺大衛·卡特懷特擊斃\N{\rOriginal Text}River Cartwright, shot by his grandfather, David Cartwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.52,0:22:34.85,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}大衛·卡特懷特\N{\rOriginal Text}David Cartwright?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:38.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但他不是我們最厲害的特工嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}But he was supposed to be one of our finest, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.31,0:22:40.06,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是從沒見過他啦 但是\N{\rOriginal Text}I mean, I never met him, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:44.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不好意思 他為什麼要槍殺親孫子\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm sorry, why on earth did he shoot his grandson?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.36,0:22:48.86,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}顯然他誤把他當成闖入者了 但弗萊特控制了調查\N{\rOriginal Text}Apparently he mistook him for an intruder, but Flyte's got it locked down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:51.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好 對了 你覺得她怎麼樣\N{\rOriginal Text}Right. How's she working out for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.66,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}很好 是了 我知道她不是你選的\N{\rOriginal Text}Good. Yes. I know she wasn't your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:55.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}她是我選的\N{\rOriginal Text}She was my choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:57.08,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}只不過她選的條件是你的\N{\rOriginal Text}It was the terms of her choosing that were yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:23:00.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我覺得你會看到 招個外人有什麼好處的 戴安娜\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I think you'll see the benefits of bringing in an outsider, Diana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:03.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}她不受任何內部政治的影響\N{\rOriginal Text}I mean, she's unswayed by any internal politics,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:06.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這些都有助於她的可信度\N{\rOriginal Text}all helps with the accountability drive, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:08.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不要把卡特懷特的事公開\N{\rOriginal Text}Let's not share this Cartwright incident with the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.93,0:23:11.72,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}在找到大衛前不要 我們知道發生了什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Not until we've found David and we know what the hell happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.72,0:23:14.72,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好的 沒錯 我能明白其中道理 真是悲劇 戴安娜\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah. No, I can see the sense in that. Tragic. Diana?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.72,0:23:15.81,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是\N{\rOriginal Text}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.81,0:23:18.44,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我在想 你會不會\N{\rOriginal Text}Was just wondering-Just wondering whether you might
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.44,0:23:21.52,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}希望替我去參加 這個政府危機應對委員會會議\N{\rOriginal Text}prefer to attend this COBRA meeting rather than me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:23.27,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這是局長的職責\N{\rOriginal Text}That's a First Desk duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:25.78,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}大家都說 你在接替蒂爾尼期間\N{\rOriginal Text}But by all accounts, you did such a sterling job
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.78,0:23:27.65,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}做得非常出色\N{\rOriginal Text}filling in after Tearney.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:30.99,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}鑒於目前的嚴峻形勢 再加上你顯然經驗豐富\N{\rOriginal Text}Given the gravity of the situation and obviously your experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:35.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我認為也許你去出席 他們會自在得多\N{\rOriginal Text}I think they'd be a lot more comfortable, you know, with you being present
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:37.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}回頭你再向我匯報 好嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}and reporting back to me. Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.25,0:23:40.08,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}當然\N{\rOriginal Text}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:43.50,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是嗎 你答應了 這 太好了 是的 你說什麼都行\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes? Is that okay? Is it o-Great. Yes. Yep. Anything you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.50,0:23:45.00,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}非常感謝 謝謝\N{\rOriginal Text}Thank you so much. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.93,0:23:55.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好了\N{\rOriginal Text}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:04.86,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你為什麼炸韋斯特艾克斯\N{\rOriginal Text}Why did you bomb Westacres?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:08.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你的組織裏有多少人\N{\rOriginal Text}How many are in your network?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:13.41,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}下一個目標是什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What is the next target?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.91,0:24:16.91,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}嘿\N{\rOriginal Text}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:20.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}下一個目標是什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What is the next target?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.37,0:24:25.59,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這就是讓嫌疑人招供的方法 讓我去審問即可\N{\rOriginal Text}That's how you get a suspect to talk. Just put me in a room with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.46,0:24:29.88,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}如果真有事瞞著你 我可以堅持更久的\N{\rOriginal Text}I could've held out longer if I was actually holding something from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.88,0:24:33.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不 所有人都有扛不住的時候 我堅持了多久\N{\rOriginal Text}No, everyone's got a breaking point. What was mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.60,0:24:38.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}七秒 就七秒\N{\rOriginal Text}Seven seconds. Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.97,0:24:41.52,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好了 給錢 見鬼\N{\rOriginal Text}Right. Pay up. Fuck's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:48.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}真好 200個\N{\rOriginal Text}Lovely. 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.23,0:24:49.44,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}行 好\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.11,0:24:53.45,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}現在我知道是什麼體驗了 我覺得我能堅持一分鐘\N{\rOriginal Text}Now I know what it's like, I reckon I could do a full minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.45,0:24:55.20,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是啊 真的\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.58,0:25:01.16,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這裏到底怎麼了 漏水了嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}What on earth's been going on here? Do we have a leak?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.16,0:25:02.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒有 他給我用水刑來著\N{\rOriginal Text}No. He's been waterboarding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.96,0:25:04.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}為什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:06.67,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}打賭 曲別針\N{\rOriginal Text}For a bet. Paper clips.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.67,0:25:09.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}曲別針是他的戒賭「鎮靜劑」\N{\rOriginal Text}Paper clips are his gambling methadone.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.59,0:25:14.18,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這個辦公室已經夠亂的了\N{\rOriginal Text}This office is in enough of a state already.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.80,0:25:19.60,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}一定要把頭髮擦乾 親愛的\N{\rOriginal Text}Do dry your hair, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.81,0:25:23.60,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}當年在總部\N{\rOriginal Text}You know, back at the Park,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.60,0:25:26.94,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是「數據庫女王」的辦公桌分配員之一\N{\rOriginal Text}I was one of the Desk Allocators to the Queens of the Database.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.94,0:25:28.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你說過了\N{\rOriginal Text}You have mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.23,0:25:30.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我依然不知道那是什麼意思\N{\rOriginal Text}Still not sure what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.19,0:25:33.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}意思就是我坐在所有部門主管的對面\N{\rOriginal Text}It means that I was across the management of every office.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.28,0:25:36.66,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我知道誰什麼時候在做什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}I knew who was doing what, when.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.66,0:25:39.70,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我覺得管理這地方更具挑戰\N{\rOriginal Text}And I find running this place more of a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.66,0:25:42.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你們打算什麼時候把聖誕裝飾收起來\N{\rOriginal Text}When are you going to pack up the Christmas decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.37,0:25:45.00,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們拋硬幣決定了 雪莉會收\N{\rOriginal Text}We flipped for it. Shirley's gonna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.00,0:25:46.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}才不是 三局兩勝\N{\rOriginal Text}No, I'm not. Best of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.04,0:25:49.59,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}趁還沒給我們惹上霉運 快把飾品收好\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, just pack them up before you bring us bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.38,0:25:52.09,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們的運氣已經不能更霉了\N{\rOriginal Text}Our luck can't get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.22,0:25:55.30,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}該死\N{\rOriginal Text}Blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.34,0:25:59.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我把這些上周的文件退給你們\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm giving you these back from last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.43,0:26:03.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}怎麼 是議會收到的噪音投訴清單\N{\rOriginal Text}What, the list of noise complaints to councils?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.23,0:26:05.89,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這些需要按日期排序 是\N{\rOriginal Text}They need to be in date order. Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.89,0:26:09.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好吧 凱瑟琳要求 這種文件按投訴數量分類 所以\N{\rOriginal Text}Right, well, Catherine wanted things like this grouped by number of complaints, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.36,0:26:12.11,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}凱瑟琳不在這裏 對嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Catherine's not here, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.07,0:26:15.07,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}隨便啦\N{\rOriginal Text}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.78,0:26:17.57,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們怎麼做都沒意義\N{\rOriginal Text}Pointless however we do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.58,0:26:22.20,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}早上好 JK 小心腳下\N{\rOriginal Text}Morning, JK. Do watch your footing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.83,0:26:25.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}還是你喜歡被稱為科\N{\rOriginal Text}Would you prefer Coe?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.54,0:26:29.71,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}科先生\N{\rOriginal Text}Mr. Coe?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.22,0:26:38.72,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他說過話嗎 一個字也沒說過\N{\rOriginal Text}Has he said anything yet? Not a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.34,0:26:41.35,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}說實話 我對他這個狀態感到很開心\N{\rOriginal Text}Which, to be honest with you, I'm pretty happy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.68,0:26:46.73,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他常常做這個動作\N{\rOriginal Text}He just does this?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.73,0:26:49.77,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}在工作間隙就做 對 所以請趕快給他點活幹吧\N{\rOriginal Text}In between work, yeah, so please give him some work quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.25,0:27:10.46,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}1.95鎊\N{\rOriginal Text}1.95.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.13,0:27:16.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}(惡魔的心態)
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.05,0:27:20.18,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼人會炸滿是顧客的購物中心啊\N{\rOriginal Text}What kind of person blows up a shopping center full of people?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.72,0:27:22.30,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}讓人不禁去想下一個目標是什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Makes you wonder what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.30,0:27:25.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是 下一個是佳發蛋糕\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes. Jaffa Cakes. That's what's next.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.97,0:27:28.56,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}再來點我可舒適\N{\rOriginal Text}And some Alka-Seltzer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.81,0:27:34.40,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}給 謝謝\N{\rOriginal Text}There you go. Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.66,0:27:42.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你們摧毀了我\N{\rOriginal Text}You have crushed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.37,0:27:47.50,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對我施暴\N{\rOriginal Text}Wreaked violence upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:52.33,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}只有現在我才能得到自由\N{\rOriginal Text}Only now will I be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.33,0:27:53.46,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}兩分鐘後抵達\N{\rOriginal Text}Two minutes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.30,0:27:59.76,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我被你們的系統囚禁多年 你們將為此付出代價\N{\rOriginal Text}You will suffer for the years I spent imprisoned by your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.14,0:28:06.35,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}上帝自有安排 我不會是最後一個\N{\rOriginal Text}God willing, I will not be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.86,0:28:18.69,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你們很快會從我兄弟們那裏聽到消息 怎麼樣\N{\rOriginal Text}You will hear from my brothers soon. Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.69,0:28:20.90,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}蘭姆確認了屍體就是瑞弗·卡特懷特\N{\rOriginal Text}Lamb identified the body as River Cartwright.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.90,0:28:21.99,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那就確定了\N{\rOriginal Text}That's confirmed, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.99,0:28:23.74,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}蘭姆給你惹麻煩了嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Lamb give you any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.74,0:28:25.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我之前對付過蘭姆這樣的男人\N{\rOriginal Text}I've dealt with men like Lamb before.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.58,0:28:26.87,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我覺得你沒有\N{\rOriginal Text}I don't think you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.87,0:28:28.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}大衛在哪 依然下落不明\N{\rOriginal Text}Where's David? Still missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.79,0:28:31.46,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}一位鄰居聽到半夜時有汽車駛離\N{\rOriginal Text}A neighbor heard a car drive off in the middle of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.46,0:28:32.88,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}可惡的卡特懷特一家\N{\rOriginal Text}Those bloody Cartwrights.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.88,0:28:35.42,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他們為什麼 非要在我們忙不過來時搞這些\N{\rOriginal Text}Why do they have to do this when we're stretched so thin?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.04,0:28:37.75,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}找到老卡特懷特\N{\rOriginal Text}Find Cartwright senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.75,0:28:39.17,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我不是該調查韋斯特艾克斯案\N{\rOriginal Text}Shouldn't I be on Westacres?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.17,0:28:41.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我聽說你們追蹤到了 炸彈襲擊者所在的公寓\N{\rOriginal Text}I heard you traced the bomber back to a flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.43,0:28:43.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}此刻正有一支武裝小隊突襲那裏\N{\rOriginal Text}There's an armed unit going in right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.47,0:28:46.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我要你去查卡特懷特謀殺案\N{\rOriginal Text}I want you on the Cartwright murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.81,0:28:51.35,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}兩分鐘後抵達 長官 有人進出公寓嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Two minutes out, ma'am. Has anyone been in or out of the flat?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.35,0:28:53.31,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們開始監視後還沒有\N{\rOriginal Text}Not since we've had eyes on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.31,0:28:57.32,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}長官 這是溫特斯 昨天下午1點剛過時出門的畫面\N{\rOriginal Text}Ma'am, this is Winters setting out just after 1:00 p.m. yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.32,0:29:00.28,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們從今天凌晨4點就開始監視了 無人機也已升空\N{\rOriginal Text}We've been on it since 4:00 a.m. today. Our drones are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.28,0:29:01.99,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}窗簾都拉上了 所以我們無法確定\N{\rOriginal Text}Curtains are drawn, so we can't be certain,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.99,0:29:03.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但據我們所知 那裏沒有其他人\N{\rOriginal Text}but as far as we know, there's no one else in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.61,0:29:06.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這不代表裏面沒人 也許有共犯\N{\rOriginal Text}Doesn't mean there isn't. Might be accomplices.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.87,0:29:09.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}把那些小孩撤離\N{\rOriginal Text}Move those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.66,0:29:12.33,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好 把那些小孩撤離\N{\rOriginal Text}Okay. Move those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.32,0:29:42.69,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}嗨 抱歉 我遲到了\N{\rOriginal Text}Hi. Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.69,0:29:44.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}後面有動靜嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}Any activity at the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.49,0:29:45.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}還是沒有 長官\N{\rOriginal Text}Still nothing, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.43,0:30:10.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}行動\N{\rOriginal Text}Proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.85,0:30:19.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}警察 阿爾法1隊進入大樓\N{\rOriginal Text}Police! Alpha-1 entering the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.19,0:30:21.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}開門了 警察\N{\rOriginal Text}Opening! Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.86,0:30:26.86,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}安全\N{\rOriginal Text}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.58,0:30:33.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}安全 安全\N{\rOriginal Text}Clear. Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:37.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}安全\N{\rOriginal Text}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.42,0:30:40.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}安全\N{\rOriginal Text}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.13,0:30:44.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}安全\N{\rOriginal Text}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.34,0:30:46.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}安全 安全\N{\rOriginal Text}Clear! Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.76,0:30:48.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}安全\N{\rOriginal Text}Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.56,0:30:56.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他活得像個和尚\N{\rOriginal Text}He lived like a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.77,0:31:00.11,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}公寓安全 長官\N{\rOriginal Text}The flat's clear, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.73,0:31:01.94,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這裏沒什麼東西\N{\rOriginal Text}There's not much to go on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.94,0:31:05.44,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}讓鑒證科的人過去 我要把那公寓翻個底朝天\N{\rOriginal Text}Get forensics in there. I want every inch of that flat turned over.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.44,0:31:06.74,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}明白\N{\rOriginal Text}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.16,0:31:12.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好 兄弟們 讓白大褂來搞科學調查吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Right, boys, let's let the white coats in here to do their science.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.58,0:31:13.66,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}長官\N{\rOriginal Text}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.70,0:31:15.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}找到一本護照\N{\rOriginal Text}I found a passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.46,0:31:18.71,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}和他用來租車的身份一致\N{\rOriginal Text}It's the same ID he used to hire the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.50,0:31:21.17,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}(羅伯特邁克爾溫特斯 英國公民)\N他沒有隱藏身份\N{\rOriginal Text}He wasn't hiding himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.38,0:31:23.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}因為他知道自己要死了\N{\rOriginal Text}Because he knew he was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.80,0:31:28.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}科學專家來了\N{\rOriginal Text}Here come the boffins.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.01,0:31:31.22,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}希望你們這些野蠻人沒有把這裏搞亂\N{\rOriginal Text}Hope you animals haven't trashed the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.22,0:31:32.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒什麼可搞亂的\N{\rOriginal Text}Nothing to trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.93,0:31:36.48,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}徹查整個公寓 有些多餘的衣物 靴子 一個睡袋\N{\rOriginal Text}Swept the whole flat, some spare clothes, boots, sleeping bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.48,0:31:37.56,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}大概就這些 對\N{\rOriginal Text}That's about it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:39.10,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}走吧 滾蛋\N{\rOriginal Text}Go on then. Fuck off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.10,0:31:40.94,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}給這裏來點光線吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Let's shed some light on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.19,0:31:46.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}該死\N{\rOriginal Text}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.78,0:31:55.24,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}出什麼事了\N{\rOriginal Text}What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.45,0:31:58.16,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我 快回答\N{\rOriginal Text}I-Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.16,0:32:01.08,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好像有炸彈陷阱 長官 老天 什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}I think there was a booby trap, ma'am. Jesus Christ. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.08,0:32:02.75,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}長官 三人死亡 見鬼\N{\rOriginal Text}Ma'am, three dead... Oh, fuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.75,0:32:03.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}可能有更多人受傷\N{\rOriginal Text}...possibly more injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.67,0:32:05.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}把人撤出來 封鎖區域\N{\rOriginal Text}Get them out. Lock it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.84,0:32:08.55,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}疏散整個街區 派一個新小隊去\N{\rOriginal Text}Evacuate the entire block, and get a new team in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.55,0:32:10.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們必須弄清有沒有第二個放炸彈的人\N{\rOriginal Text}We need to know if there's a second bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.93,0:32:11.93,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是 長官\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.72,0:32:15.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}見鬼 這真是一場災難\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, fuck. This is a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.01,0:32:16.97,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}徹頭徹尾的災難\N{\rOriginal Text}Absolute bloody disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.81,0:32:19.89,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}克勞德\N{\rOriginal Text}Claude.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.02,0:32:23.48,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}克勞德\N{\rOriginal Text}Claude?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.98,0:32:27.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}抱歉 我從沒見過這種事\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm sorry. I've just never seen anything quite like this
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.36,0:32:30.65,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}發生在我眼前 我 是 但你必須承擔責任\N{\rOriginal Text}in front of my own eyes before, so I-Yeah, but you need to shoulder it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.32,0:32:32.45,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對 你說得對\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.87,0:32:39.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我最好再向首相匯報一下 發表一份聲明\N{\rOriginal Text}I suppose I better update the PM again and issue a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.12,0:32:41.67,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不 你必須先通知家屬\N{\rOriginal Text}No. You have to tell the families first.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.67,0:32:43.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他們不能從新聞上得知此事\N{\rOriginal Text}They can't find out about this on the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.58,0:32:44.71,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}當然\N{\rOriginal Text}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.71,0:32:49.05,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我不知道自己剛才 謝謝你 戴安娜 你太可靠了\N{\rOriginal Text}I don't know what I was-Thank you, Diana. You're a real rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.38,0:32:51.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}情況更新\N{\rOriginal Text}Where's my update?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.76,0:32:55.39,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}正在疏散樓裏的人 長官\N{\rOriginal Text}Evacuating the building now, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.68,0:33:00.14,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}真是一團糟\N{\rOriginal Text}What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.99,0:33:20.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}羅迪裏克 在\N{\rOriginal Text}Roderick? Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.79,0:33:22.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你在幹什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.54,0:33:25.00,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}拿走卡特懷特的電腦\N{\rOriginal Text}Taking Cartwright's computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.54,0:33:27.54,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}為什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.71,0:33:30.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}因為他死了\N{\rOriginal Text}Because he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.72,0:33:33.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼 怎麼了\N{\rOriginal Text}What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.26,0:33:35.64,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你在幹什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.64,0:33:37.72,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}羅迪說瑞弗死了\N{\rOriginal Text}Roddy just said that River's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.56,0:33:39.77,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這玩笑不好笑 何\N{\rOriginal Text}Sick joke, Ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.81,0:33:42.77,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不是玩笑 是事實\N{\rOriginal Text}It's not a joke. It's a fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.64,0:33:46.15,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你怎麼知道的 蘭姆告訴我的\N{\rOriginal Text}How would you know? Lamb told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.15,0:33:47.48,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}蘭姆告訴你什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Lamb told you what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.48,0:33:48.90,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這裏是什麼情況\N{\rOriginal Text}What's going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.90,0:33:50.40,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}卡特懷特死了\N{\rOriginal Text}Cartwright's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.07,0:33:52.99,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼叫他死了 哈哈 很好笑\N{\rOriginal Text}What do you mean he's dead? Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.99,0:33:55.74,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}蘭姆告訴我說卡特懷特死了\N{\rOriginal Text}Lamb told me Cartwright's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.03,0:33:59.24,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}「我會晚點進辦公室\N{\rOriginal Text}"Will be late in.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.66,0:34:03.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}昨晚通宵鑒定卡特懷特的屍體」\N{\rOriginal Text}Up all night identifying Cartwright's body."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.04,0:34:05.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}一定是玩笑 拜託 什麼 在哪 怎麼回事\N{\rOriginal Text}It's got to be a windup. Come on. What? Where? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.25,0:34:06.33,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他一定在笑呢\N{\rOriginal Text}He must be having a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.33,0:34:09.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這根本說不通啊 你跟蘭姆說過話嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}This doesn't make any sense. Have you spoken to Lamb?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.13,0:34:10.50,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒有 所以\N{\rOriginal Text}No. So--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.50,0:34:12.51,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什 你認為他死了 但你要偷他的電腦\N{\rOriginal Text}Wha-So you think he's dead, but you nick his computer?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.51,0:34:15.22,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這不叫偷他的電腦 他死了\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm not nicking his computer. He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.22,0:34:18.30,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}任務日誌上說大衛·卡特懷特家有槍擊報告\N{\rOriginal Text}Duty log says shots reported at David Cartwright's.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.18,0:34:21.27,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}發現屍體\N{\rOriginal Text}Body found.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:34.57,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我的天\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.28,0:34:38.45,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我的天\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.37,0:34:41.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}該死 這都怪我\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, shit. This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.37,0:34:43.62,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}天啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.62,0:34:46.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}天啊 我叫他去的 去哪\N{\rOriginal Text}Oh, my God. I told him to go. Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.25,0:34:50.25,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我叫他去看看爺爺 他爺爺開槍把他打死了\N{\rOriginal Text}I told him to go and see his grandfather, and his grandfather fucking shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.25,0:34:53.30,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}見鬼 這不是真的 什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}Fuck. Tell me this isn't true. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.30,0:34:55.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}竟然又發生了\N{\rOriginal Text}Tell me this is not happening again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.92,0:34:59.39,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不 怎麼又出這種事啊 我們甚至還不瞭解情況\N{\rOriginal Text}No, this is not happening again. We don't even know the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.39,0:35:02.35,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們知道他死了 不是嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}We know he's dead, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.85,0:35:04.60,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我們還需要瞭解什麼 他死了\N{\rOriginal Text}What else do we need to know? He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.65,0:35:13.23,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}說個好消息吧 我有女朋友了\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, in happier news, I have a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.57,0:35:17.70,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你這個王八蛋\N{\rOriginal Text}You're a fucking prick!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.70,0:35:18.78,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}路易莎\N{\rOriginal Text}Loui-Louisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.28,0:35:21.58,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好痛\N{\rOriginal Text}Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.87,0:35:30.67,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}心平氣和地接受現實吧 你錯過機會了\N{\rOriginal Text}Make your peace. You missed your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.08,0:36:05.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}倫敦反恐警察和安全部門確認\N{\rOriginal Text}Counterterrorism police and the security service
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.79,0:36:08.00,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他們在追查\N{\rOriginal Text}in London have confirmed they are following
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.00,0:36:11.54,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}馬修阿姆羅利瓦拉 繼續調查\N{\rOriginal Text}all potential leads as the investigation into the bombing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.54,0:36:13.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}韋斯特艾克斯購物中心爆炸案\N{\rOriginal Text}of the Westacres Shopping Center continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.59,0:36:17.80,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}然而一位發言人證實 他們不知道羅伯特·溫特斯\N{\rOriginal Text}Whilst a spokesperson confirmed they don't know how Robert Winters
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.80,0:36:20.59,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是如何獲取他所使用的裝置所需原料的\N{\rOriginal Text}acquired the ingredients for the device he used,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.59,0:36:24.39,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}據瞭解 居民們\N{\rOriginal Text}it's understood that residents...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.39,0:36:27.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}一直在配合警方詢問\N{\rOriginal Text}...have been assisting police with their inquiries.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.47,0:36:29.81,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}同時 25歲的傑克·沃頓\N{\rOriginal Text}Meanwhile 25-year-old Jack Wharton
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.81,0:36:33.56,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是最新公佈姓名的襲擊受害者\N{\rOriginal Text}is the latest victim killed in the attack to be named.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.56,0:36:36.82,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}據報道 他的兄弟在爆炸中受傷\N{\rOriginal Text}His brother was reportedly injured by the blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.82,0:36:39.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}至此 全部23名爆炸案遇難者的身份\N{\rOriginal Text}This means that all the 23 people who died
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.36,0:36:42.07,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}都已經確定\N{\rOriginal Text}in the bombing have now been identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.87,0:36:45.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}今早 武裝警察巡邏幾條主要\N{\rOriginal Text}This morning, armed police patrolled several major...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.83,0:36:48.12,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}傑克遜 你想怎樣\N{\rOriginal Text}Jackson, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.70,0:36:51.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}這個歡迎很熱烈啊 你可以加點感情進去的\N{\rOriginal Text}That's a nice welcome. You could have put some feeling into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.83,0:36:54.67,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我加了 只不過不是你想要的那種\N{\rOriginal Text}I did, just not the kind you were hoping for.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.09,0:36:58.17,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}打算邀請我進來嗎 不打算\N{\rOriginal Text}Gonna invite me in? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.17,0:36:59.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那我強行進來呢\N{\rOriginal Text}Mind if I come in anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.22,0:37:09.47,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我帶了早餐來\N{\rOriginal Text}I brought breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.47,0:37:11.85,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我吃過了 而且那不叫早餐\N{\rOriginal Text}I've already eaten, and that's not a breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.56,0:37:13.94,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那喝一杯如何\N{\rOriginal Text}How about a drink then?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.52,0:37:15.98,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}就算對你來說 現在喝也早了點\N{\rOriginal Text}Bit early, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.23,0:37:18.69,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我是說喝一杯水\N{\rOriginal Text}I meant a glass of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.28,0:37:26.41,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你來幹嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}So, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.24,0:37:29.91,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}就不能來看看老朋友\N{\rOriginal Text}Can't drop in on an old friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.91,0:37:31.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}不太可能 這麼說也不對\N{\rOriginal Text}Unlikely and inaccurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.08,0:37:36.42,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我剛剛鑒定完瑞弗·卡特懷特的屍體\N{\rOriginal Text}I've just come from identifying River Cartwright's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.42,0:37:39.21,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我想第一個告訴你\N{\rOriginal Text}I wanted you to be the first to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.88,0:37:43.34,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}看吧 瞧 早餐 裏面有橙子呢\N{\rOriginal Text}There, you see? Look, breakfast. Got orange in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.34,0:37:45.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}水果 有益健康 瑞弗 怎麼會\N{\rOriginal Text}Fruit. Healthy. River? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.89,0:37:49.06,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}胸口和臉部中槍\N{\rOriginal Text}Bullet to the chest and a bullet to the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.06,0:37:51.10,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}整個討人厭的表情都沒了\N{\rOriginal Text}Literally wiped the annoying look off it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.35,0:37:57.48,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你聽了都沒反應嗎 這就是我的反應\N{\rOriginal Text}Aren't you going to respond? This is me responding.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.82,0:38:01.03,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}在哪發生的\N{\rOriginal Text}Where did it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.49,0:38:03.99,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}洗手間裏\N{\rOriginal Text}In the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.61,0:38:06.37,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}跟當年一樣 是吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Just like old times, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.37,0:38:09.41,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你打算告訴其他人嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}And will you tell the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.41,0:38:10.83,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我給何發了條短信\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I sent a text to Ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.83,0:38:13.62,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我想他現在應該已經告訴大家了\N{\rOriginal Text}I expect he'd have spread the word around by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.62,0:38:15.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你發了條短信\N{\rOriginal Text}You sent a text?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.54,0:38:16.92,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我可沒打算發推文\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I wasn't gonna tweet it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.92,0:38:19.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}老天 斯坦迪什 人命關天啊\N{\rOriginal Text}Jesus Christ, Standish, a man died.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.04,0:38:21.51,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你知道這消息 會給路易莎帶來多大打擊嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}You know what this news will do to Louisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.51,0:38:24.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}所以我才發給何 我很講究策略的\N{\rOriginal Text}That's why I sent it to Ho. I know how to be tactful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.18,0:38:31.68,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}那麼 既然你已經告訴我 這個壞消息了 你可以走了\N{\rOriginal Text}So-Well, now that you've told me this terrible news, y-feel free to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.06,0:38:36.56,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}能看出來 你很忙\N{\rOriginal Text}I can see you're busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.98,0:38:44.82,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你就不問問是誰的洗手間嗎 誰的\N{\rOriginal Text}Aren't you gonna ask whose bathroom? Whose bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.57,0:38:47.49,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}抱歉 只能告訴需要知道的人\N{\rOriginal Text}Sorry, need-to-know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.49,0:38:48.74,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你很開心吧\N{\rOriginal Text}You're enjoying this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.74,0:38:51.70,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}能喝杯水就更開心了\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I'd enjoy it more with a glass of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.70,0:38:54.54,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你知道通宵不睡的人有多缺水\N{\rOriginal Text}You know how dehydrated you get after an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.04,0:38:56.29,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}老天\N{\rOriginal Text}For God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.22,0:39:11.51,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你一個人住\N{\rOriginal Text}Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.47,0:39:14.22,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對 我該先問問的\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, I should have asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.22,0:39:16.27,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我看起來像有伴的樣子\N{\rOriginal Text}Do I look like I have company?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.27,0:39:18.73,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好吧 我必須問的\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah. Well, I had to ask, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.73,0:39:22.82,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}有些污名可不好洗刷 你應該知道\N{\rOriginal Text}It's hard to shake off a reputation. Well, you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.82,0:39:25.82,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你認識的每一個人都認為你是個大混蛋\N{\rOriginal Text}I mean, everyone you've ever met has pegged you as an utter bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.82,0:39:29.36,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但我不用受你氣了 因為我辭職了 記得嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}But I don't have to put up with you anymore because I quit. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.37,0:39:34.29,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}至少我嘗試辭職了 我給人事部寫了三封同樣的信\N{\rOriginal Text}Well, I tried to. I've written the same letter to HR three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.29,0:39:36.50,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是 我知道 他們總把信轉發給我\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, I know. They keep forwarding it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.50,0:39:38.79,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}文件總得有人批嘛\N{\rOriginal Text}Something about ratifying the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.79,0:39:41.13,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}老天 蘭姆 問題到底出在哪\N{\rOriginal Text}For God's sake, Lamb. What's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.13,0:39:44.84,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你多年來一直刺激我 然後我終於做了讓你如願以償的事\N{\rOriginal Text}I mean, you spent years goading me, and then I finally did what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.59,0:39:48.18,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}在該死的辭職信上簽字啊 讓我繼續過我的人生\N{\rOriginal Text}Just sign the damn papers, and let me get on with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.18,0:39:50.55,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我想確保你瞭解自己的心意\N{\rOriginal Text}I wanna make sure you know your own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.26,0:39:52.60,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對 想像一下\N{\rOriginal Text}Right, imagine how I'd feel
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.60,0:39:54.85,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}如果你後悔不已 酒癮復發 我該有多難受\N{\rOriginal Text}if you wound up full of regret and had a relapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.85,0:39:56.43,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我可不想背負這種良心債\N{\rOriginal Text}I wouldn't want that on my conscience,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.43,0:39:59.35,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你會整天以淚洗面 借酒消愁\N{\rOriginal Text}you getting all weepy and hitting the bottle.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.35,0:40:02.19,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}人們說酒鬼都在找借口\N{\rOriginal Text}Now, they say drunks are just looking for an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.19,0:40:04.11,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我不怪你 這是一種病\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm not blaming you, it's a disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.11,0:40:06.07,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}對了 是他爺爺的\N{\rOriginal Text}It was his grandfather's, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.78,0:40:07.82,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.32,0:40:13.41,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他爺爺的洗手間 不是因為你問我才說的\N{\rOriginal Text}His grandfather's bathroom, not that you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.41,0:40:15.33,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你也沒問是誰\N{\rOriginal Text}You also didn't ask who.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.33,0:40:18.96,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}什麼誰 誰槍殺了瑞弗\N{\rOriginal Text}Who what? Who shot River.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.96,0:40:21.04,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}因為你和我一樣 知道他還活著\N{\rOriginal Text}Because, like me, you know he's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.00,0:40:24.42,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}別耍花樣了\N{\rOriginal Text}So stop playing games.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.42,0:40:27.01,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你剛剛告訴我說 你確認是他的屍體\N{\rOriginal Text}You've just told me you'd identified his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.01,0:40:30.88,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是啊 你對當時的情況表現得非常不在意\N{\rOriginal Text}Yeah, and you were remarkably incurious about the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.55,0:40:33.18,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}我驚呆了 好嗎\N{\rOriginal Text}I'm in shock, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.89,0:40:36.39,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你驚訝的是我來了 而不是\N{\rOriginal Text}You're in shock at me being here, but you're not in shock
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.39,0:40:39.14,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}瑞弗還活著 因為你見過他\N{\rOriginal Text}at the idea of River being alive because you've seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.14,0:40:40.69,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你在說什麼\N{\rOriginal Text}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.69,0:40:42.02,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}一派胡言 才不是\N{\rOriginal Text}That's absolute rubbish. No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.02,0:40:43.44,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}拜託 斯坦迪什 不\N{\rOriginal Text}Please, Standish. No--
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.44,0:40:45.52,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你很不擅長這一套\N{\rOriginal Text}You're no good at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.65,0:40:48.15,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}再說了\N{\rOriginal Text}And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.74,0:40:51.61,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}他的車就停在外面\N{\rOriginal Text}his car's outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.12,0:40:59.91,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}是的 好吧 他來過\N{\rOriginal Text}Yes. Okay. He was here,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.91,0:41:02.62,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}但現在不在這裏了 好 這還差不多\N{\rOriginal Text}but he's not here anymore. All right, that's better.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.62,0:41:05.50,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}好了 請別裝了\N{\rOriginal Text}Now, please don't pretend
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.50,0:41:08.46,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你一定把那個老混蛋藏在臥室了\N{\rOriginal Text}you haven't got the old bastard stashed away in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.46,0:41:10.55,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}傑克遜 瑞弗叫我保護他\N{\rOriginal Text}Jackson. River asked me to protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.22,0:41:15.22,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}滿意了\N{\rOriginal Text}Happy now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.47,0:41:18.18,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你是瞭解我的\N{\rOriginal Text}You know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.18,0:41:20.85,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}知道我什麼時候不是滿心歡喜\N{\rOriginal Text}When am I not full of joie de fucking vivre.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.85,0:41:22.94,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}很好 你現在就從我的臥室裏出去吧\N{\rOriginal Text}Good. Well, perhaps you could leave my bedroom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.94,0:41:24.02,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}嘿\N{\rOriginal Text}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.94,0:41:26.94,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}哥們\N{\rOriginal Text}Mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.03,0:41:32.20,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}瑞弗在哪\N{\rOriginal Text}Where's River?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.96,0:41:50.38,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}(巴黎德士)
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.09,0:41:53.34,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}你到底是誰\N{\rOriginal Text}Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.93,0:41:57.68,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}還有多久到\N{\rOriginal Text}How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.68,0:41:59.52,Translated Text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei Light}沒多遠了\N{\rOriginal Text}We aren't far now.
